data.description: Looking for move in ready and well cared for? If yes look no further than this Franklin Ranch on over a half acre lot! Per seller new private well within last 5 years, roof 5 years old, 200 amp electric, ac & furnace are new and leaf filter gutter guards have been installed. Basement is partially finished including a flex room! 2 car attached garage. All this for 315k in Franklin.
